Package: perturbseqR
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Loading and Manipulating Single-Cell Experiments
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Thomas", "Norman", role = c("aut")),
      person("Jander", "Kugelman", email = "jkugelm2@jh.edu", role = c("cre"))
    )
Description: An R reimplementation of the Perturbseq library for analysis of single-cell 
    experiments. Includes utilities for normalization, dimensionality reduction, 
    differential expression, and visualization of single-cell data.
